::DarkMouse::

"OK then.  Ready Commanders.  I'm very proud of this.  I only hope that you 
both like it. I tried to think of everything.  But I'm sure you two can 
think of things that I may have not have thought of.  Please let me know of 
any improvements that I may do on the tunnel for you."
She looked at both Scorponok and Quickstrike.
She felt ashamed for some reason.  She looked at the ground and turned and 
started walking down the tunnel.

She raised her head and pointed to scanners all through the tunnel.
"We can monitor these at the main computer console."
Her voice wan't quite as cheery as it was a few minutes ago.  She tried her 
best to hide her feelings.
